Minerva is a programmer's text editor written in C++/Qt. It is released under GPLv3.
To build and run follow these steps:
	$ mkdir build && cd build
	$ cmake ..
	$ make -j2
	$ ./src/minerva

To install:
	$ mkdir build && cd build
	$ cmake ..
	$ make -j2
	$ sudo make install
Or if you prefer a deb:
	$ cmake -DCPACK_GENERATORS=DEB ..
	$ make package

